{"tid":1868423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解搞罷工要投票？","createTime":"2020-02-07T14:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T15:27:54.000Z","uid":61484,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80ee800cebd5ff9962e394f2de495ba4f215ca1f","tid":1868423,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"當日三千票同意<br />\n代表最少有三千人覺得人地有野做得不足<br />\n公會為左保障呢三千人既權益先搞罷工，從來唔會講多數少數<br />\n<br />\n結果今日又係投票<br />\n同意就冇乜點多，反對就彈多左三千幾票出黎<br />\n咁嗰三千個點，冇保障？冇人權？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇住佢冇ppe 做dirty job?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁不如搞個投票批鬥嗰三千人分佢地份人工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你就算只係有一個人比公司打壓，公會都要幫佢出頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果公會行動都要投票既話，我係公司、政府、藍絲團體一定會比足資金入會買票<br />\n計翻數，我當月薪&gt;$15000<br />\n年費$1000都只係0.56%<br />\n人人都比得起<br />\n<br />\n投票唔work既理由好簡單，因為公會唔會只有單一立場既人，就咁對家數下都有：<br />\n1. 冇罷工既做埋你既野而不滿，出嚟投票<br />\n2. 政府買票<br />\n3. 藍絲<br />\n4. 大愛撚，道德撚<br />\n<br />\nin short, haea冇撚腦/間諜搞大台比人打冧再收皮<br />\n嬲撚到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb48fd57d765f975d6ce37e8e3d224c1de56e1c","tid":1868423,"uid":128748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:38:50.000Z","msg":"咁爭取雙普選嚟做咩"},{"pid":"c309cd01b2e119261ef3e35b96c419024def5f75","tid":1868423,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T15:16:03.000Z","msg":"一定係少數服從多數<br />\n如果有藍屍入工會<br />\n然後要求支持政府唔通又聽佢地話？"},{"pid":"e6f9b5e2d5fbbe21813592747253626b5872649e","tid":1868423,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T15:27:54.000Z","msg":"好多人罷左，但今次投反對<br />\n跟住成班連登仔屈人五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}